Package: abbey
Version: 0.1.0
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libc6, libsqlite3-0
Maintainer: Abbey Developer <abbey@example.com>
Description: A focused writing app for freeform flow and essays
 Abbey is a distraction-free writing application featuring:
  - Flow Mode for timed writing sessions
  - Flow Journal to read past sessions
  - Essay management with drafts and archives
  - pCloud sync integration
  - Multiple themes
